[10:59] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'is Morph. This tool is a bit more technical, but in terms of plugins that literally help you build faster, this is the one. When you\'re using Claude, it spends a lot of time and money on three things. First, editing files. Second, searching through files. And three,'

[11:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'managing context so it has the correct memory. What Morph does is it speeds up each of these processes. First, fast apply speeds up editing files up to eight times faster and 90% cheaper. Two, warp grep speeds up searching a code'

[11:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'base 50% cheaper 28% faster. And three, compact saves you 5 to 15 minutes on session compression. I\'m saying a lot of buzzwords, I get it. Let\'s simplify this. Let\'s say you go back and forth with Claude 50 times working on an app'

[11:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and it ends up editing 10 files and searching the code base five times. In theory, without Morph this could cost $3.50 and take 25 minutes. With Morph it could cost 80 cents and take about 10'

